A curated lofi hip hop experience designed for ${mixMood.toLowerCase()} moments.

Grab a coffee, settle in, and let the waves of sound wash over you.

Tracklist & Timestamps:
${timestamps.join('\n')}

About the mix:
This ambient journey was carefully constructed using AI generative synthesis to evoke a specific Lo-Fi aesthetic. Each transition is calculated with a ${crossfade}s crossfade for seamless listening.

#lofi #studybeats #relaxing #ambient #${mixMood.toLowerCase()}`;

    setExportData({
      timestampList: timestamps.join('\n'),
      youtubeDescription: description,
      m3uContent: "#EXTM3U\n" + mixTracks.map(t => `#EXTINF:${t.durationSeconds},${t.title}\n${t.audioUrl}`).join('\n'),
      jsonConfig: JSON.stringify({ name: mixName, tracks: jsonTracks, crossfade, totalDuration: totalDurationSeconds }, null, 2),
      titleSuggestion: `lofi hip hop radio — beats to ${mixMood.toLowerCase()}/relax to [${Math.floor(totalDurationSeconds/3600)} HOUR MIX]`,
      thumbnailPrompt: `Lofi anime girl sitting by a window, ${mixMood === Mood.RAINY ? 'rain drops on glass' : mixMood === Mood.NIGHT ? 'city lights at night' : 'soft afternoon sun'}, warm aesthetic, purple and amber tones, high detail, studio ghibli style`
    });
